## How It Works

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Store as ChatStore
    participant Agent as SQLAgent
    participant LLM as OpenAI

    U->>FE: Sends question
    FE->>API: POST /chat {question, conversation_id}
    API->>Store: get_history_for_llm(conv_id)
    Store-->>API: Last 20 Q&A pairs
    API->>Store: save user message
    API->>Agent: chat(question, history)
    Agent->>LLM: system_prompt + history + question
    LLM-->>Agent: SQL + response
    Agent-->>API: result
    API->>Store: save assistant message + SQL metadata
    API-->>FE: {answer, sql, data, conversation_id}
    FE->>FE: Update chat UI + sidebar
```

